No. -. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Jared Flagg, Petitioner. Submitted October 19, 1914. Decided October 26, 1914. Mr. Robert C. Beatty and Mr. Wade H. Ellis for the petitioner. The' Attorney General, The Solicitor General, and Mr. Assistant Attorney General Wallace opposing.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of prohibition or mandamus denied.
